# FINAL NOTES

This architecture uses:

* ONE persistent MPV engine
* ONE IPC socket
* ONE active mode script
* ONE launcher lifecycle

This prevents:

* duplicate keypad readers
* phantom launches
* unstable playback
* socket conflicts

The system is designed for:

* live visual performance
* instant playback
* modular expansion
* Raspberry Pi deployment

Pi-GATO V11 became the first stable GOLDENSCRIPT architecture.
